snippet.title: Super Mega Neo Pug 1.2 Teaser
snippet.description:
Super Mega Neo Pug 1.2 is here!
Enjoy additional content such as:

- Brand new characters, each with a unique perk!
- Two new biomes with unique enemies and obstacles!
- New original songs!
- New power ups to pick up and eight new trophies to collect!
- Bug fixes and optimisation.
